1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. d3 Bc5 5. c3 O-O 6. O-O Re8 7. Nbd2 a6 8.
Bxc6 dxc6 9. Nc4 Nd7 10. Qc2 Bd6 11. d4 Qe7 12. Re1 c5 13. dxe5 Nxe5 14. Nfxe5
