1. e4 e5 2. Nc3 Nc6 3. f4 exf4 4. d4 $5 {Steinitz Gambit} d5 5. exd5 Qh4+ 6.
Ke2 Qe7+ 7. Kf2 (7. Kf3 Qh4 8. Ke2 Qe7+ 9. Kf3 $10 {Steinitz-Mackenzie New
York 1883}) 7... Qh4+ 8. g3 fxg3+ 9. Kg2 Nxd4 (9... Bd6 10. Qe1+ Nce7 11. hxg3
Qxd4 12. Nf3 {12.Rh4= Steinitz-Tschigorin London 1883} Qb6 13. Be3 Qxb2 14. Bd3
Bb4 15. Bd4 f6 16. Rb1 Bxc3 17. Bxc3 Qxa2 18. Rb5 $40 {>> Analyse R.Steel
Calcutta Steinitz}) 10. hxg3 (10. Qe1+ Be7 11. hxg3 Nxc2 $13 {Steinitz}) 10...
Qg4 11. Qe1+ Be7 12. Bd3 {/\ 13.Rh4 +- Seinitz} (12. Rh4 Nxc2 13. Qe5 Qg6 14.
Rb1 Qf6 15. Bb5+ (15. Qxc7 Ne1+ 16. Kh2 Qxf1 $19) 15... Kd8 $17 {Steinitz})
